{"tid":2412137,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"給黎智英天天寫家書 　長情寫信師：他是我「沒有血緣的家人」","createTime":"2021-02-18T00:22:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T00:29:41.000Z","uid":271829,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1e47e0e0b66d6662d7056a7e3f2b979ed48ddc77","tid":2412137,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T00:22:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JzkJN2zMCKCJhBpNoiT02f2ZwCM=/1280x507/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JTDUP5XE5VCIJNMFJMSMWA673M.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJzkJN2zMCKCJhBpNoiT02f2ZwCM%3D%2F1280x507%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJTDUP5XE5VCIJNMFJMSMWA673M.jpeg&h=d914bba2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2019年反送中運動，Karmen遠在美國，每日工作時都偷偷用手機看直播，又聯絡當地港人組織參與遊行。受訪者提供相片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QpuhmtYyfeu4kUCDBLTJ034Iqjk=/1024x768/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QH5TDRVEU5CXXJD2ZA64LCT5ZY.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQpuhmtYyfeu4kUCDBLTJ034Iqjk%3D%2F1024x768%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQH5TDRVEU5CXXJD2ZA64LCT5ZY.jpeg&h=6bb3e91e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國推動香港人權與民主法案之際，Karmen自製文宣，又不斷遊說身邊的美國人，讓他們了解香港的情況。受訪者提供相片<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n九七主權移交前夕，當時只有十來歲的Karmen隨父母舉家移民到美國，「父母一聽到中英談判，就知一定要走」，多年來在美留學、工作以至成家，然而「到底我係香港人定美國人」這個疑問一直未散，直至2014年催淚煙瀰漫，她毫不猶豫回港，在金鐘夏愨道與年輕人一起「執垃圾」，才驚覺「香港人」這個身份早已深入血肉，「有啲嘢係抹唔走，放唔低」。<br />\n反送中期間，Karmen因事未能回港；香港每日烽火連天，遠在美國的她同樣受盡煎熬，「每日日頭返工就偷偷哋睇live，夜晚瞓覺又擔心香港新一日嘅示威」。每日被憤怒及無力感充斥心頭，她一直在想，「到底有啲咩可以做？」遂聯絡當地港人組織、參與遊行，亦去信當地參議員要求支持《香港人權與民主法案》。<br />\n<br />\n視黃店職員如家人：好多嘢一講就明<br />\n遠在他國，未能親身為運動出一分力，Karmen以自己的方式支持香港，以貴3至5成的價錢，越洋光顧香港的黃店，再以速遞寄回美國，亦因此與不少黃店職員成為好友，「因為大家都係香港人，好多嘢一講就明，傾一陣就可以好friend&hellip;&hellip;係香港先畀到呢啲朋友我」，她頓了一頓，更正：「係無血緣嘅屋企人。」<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210218/5B5KL7EI2BFNNA5O6IAUJ32O2U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210218%2F5B5KL7EI2BFNNA5O6IAUJ32O2U%2F&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOmL0CtalYwMF7My3GtbBKd0%3D&h=8fad33b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210218%2F5B5KL7EI2BFNNA5O6IAUJ32O2U%2F&h=a82746eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210218/5B5KL7EI2BFNNA5O6IAUJ32O2U/</a>"},{"pid":"3f3fedc78ed3d617f6c92f691a513896a28d432f","tid":2412137,"uid":18724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T00:29:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}